	<<= ($pronoun is "m" and maleChance($pronoun) lt 100) or ($pronoun is "f" and maleChance($pronoun) gt 0) ? "의기소침한 듯 보인다" : "눈을 굴린다">>. "어쨌든. 그냥 여기서 나가, 변태야!"
